title: DON'T MISS: Photos of stunning Ferrari SF70H F1 car | Zee News
text:
New Delhi: Formula one giants Ferrari have unveiled their 2017 challenger on Friday via an online video. 
Named Ferrari SF70H, it will be driven by Sebastian Vettel and Kimi Raik​​konen. 
This stunning machine features a shark fin cover that is predominantly white while the rest of the car is well Ferrari red. 
Other distinctive feature of the car is its high wing forward of the rear wing, called T-wing. 
Ferrari are the sixth team to unveil their cars this week. 
First Published: Friday, February 24, 2017 - 23:05 More from zeenews
